OL,3,CMum slams 'medical negligence' after
OL,4,Cson's wait for life-changing procedure
OL,6,FEuan's frustrated mum Eleanor, 49,
OL,7,Fsaid her son is permanently seeing
OL,8,Fdouble which is having a "devastating
OL,9,Feffect on his life at home and at
OL,10,Fschool".
OL,12,FAnd she has accused the health board
OL,13,Fof "medical negligence" for leaving
OL,14,FEuan ` who had surgery for a malignant
OL,15,Fbrain tumour a decade ago ` "in limbo".
OL,17,FSpeaking to Media Scotland she said:
OL,18,F"After an accidental bang to the head
OL,19,Fin 2021, Euan was left with a squint
OL,20,Fand persistent double vision.
