OL,3,CMum slams 'medical negligence' after
OL,4,Cson's wait for life-changing procedure
OL,6,F"Medical staff were informed back then
OL,7,Fbut it wasn't until last May that he
OL,8,Fwas finally put on a list for a small
OL,9,Fprocedure to inject botox into his
OL,10,Feye, so that the surgeon can see how
OL,11,Ffar it needs to be moved to fix the
OL,12,Fsquint in a further operation.
OL,14,F"But he's still waiting and we don't
OL,15,Fknow how much longer it's going to be
OL,16,Ffor.
OL,18,F"We don't seem to be any further
OL,19,Fforward since 2021 and it just feels
OL,20,Flike medical negligence now."
