OL,11,Fbeen told he can't be referred to any
OL,12,Fother health board in Scotland for the
OL,13,Fprocedure.
OL,15,F"We could go private, but it would
OL,16,Fprobably need to be done in Newcastle
OL,17,Fby the surgeon who would be doing it
OL,18,Fin Dumfries.
