OL,6,F"My husband and I have paid national
OL,7,Finsurance all our lives for NHS
OL,8,Ftreatment and Euan is still just a
OL,9,Fchild.
OL,11,F"I've complained to the health board
OL,12,Fand their final response was that the
OL,13,Fspecialist surgeon only comes to the
OL,14,Fhospital once a month and only if
OL,15,Fthere's a free theatre and available
OL,16,Fstaff to cover.
OL,18,F"All we want is a resolution to this
OL,19,Fso that Euan can start to live his
OL,20,Flife again."
